---
import Button from "./Button.astro";
import selfie from "../images/selfie-lg.jpeg";
---

<div class="flex">
  <h2 class="text-6xl mb-10">Bio</h2>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20">
  <div class="leading-relaxed text-lg">
    <p>
      James is a JavaScript Developer, Speaker, and Teacher with a passion for
      teaching developers through various mediums of content. He is a firm
      believer in work-life balance, the on-going pursuit of personal happiness,
      and empowering others to take control of their career. His personal
      philosophy of “Learn Build Teach” has blossomed into a growing community
      of aspiring and established developers focused on helping each succeed.
    </p>
    <br />
    <p>
      His professional experience includes Software Development at Fedex and
      Developer Advocacy at Microsoft, Auth0, and PlanetScale. He is currently
      working as a full-time Technical Content Creator focused on growing his
      YouTube audience of over 150k subscribers, a weekly Web Development
      podcast called Compressed.fm, and an array of online courses. James has
      partnered with notable companies like Cloudflare, Microsoft, Fauna,
      Cloudinary, and more along his content creation journey. In his spare
      time, James plays co-ed soccer with his wife, spends time with his dogs,
      and can solve a Rubik's cube in under a minute.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div>
    <Button
      classStr="mt-4 inline-block"
      text="Download Headshot"
      download
      href="/images/selfie-square.jpeg"
      isLink
    />
  </div>
</div>
